    <H2>January 1999</H2>
    <UL>

    <li><b><a href="http://www.oreilly.com">O'Reilly and Associates</a>
    January 1999</b><br>
    <a href="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/opensources/book/kirkmck.html">
